---
title: Central American Style Spiced Cottage Pie with Cheesy Spring Onion Mash Top and Garlic Peas
description: This Central American Style Spiced Cottage Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
